y":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:39:57.000Z","msg":"香港金總終於接受網上會員申請啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62ad5e20e3fab2a657f6d8975c6aa8a696a0059c","tid":1787490,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共狗真係唔撚學精</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}